snippet.title: Calmed by the Dark Leviathan - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Calmed by the Dark Leviathan launches July 2nd for PC.
Music by YouFulca: https://wingless-seraph.net/en/index.html
Calmed by the Dark Leviathan is open-world game about killing giant monsters while using giant robots and also giant monsters...
